OL,4,C'My husband refused a divorce for nine
OL,5,Cyears'
OL,6, Rifka Meyer was 32 when she entered
OL,7, into a religious marriage.
OL,8, Two-and-a-half years later, she became
OL,9, what is known among orthodox Jews as a
OL,10, "chained wife" - trapped in a religious
OL,11, marriage with a man who refused to let
OL,12, her have a divorce.
OL,14,F"You feel hopeless and you feel very
OL,15,Falone," she tells BBC Newsnight. "You
OL,16,Ffeel like you're screaming and not
OL,17,Fbeing heard."
